H0.text: The Red Setter is more properly known by which name. Irish Setter

H1.text: The Red Setter is more properly known by which name. English Setter

H2.text: The Red Setter is more properly known by which name. Gordon Setter

H3.text: The Red Setter is more properly known by which name. Red setter

A4.text: The Irish Setter (Irish: sotar rua, literally 'red setter') is a setter, a breed of gundog, and family dog originating in Ireland.

A5.text: The term Irish Setter is commonly used to encompass the show-bred dog recognised by the American Kennel Club as well as the field-bred Red Setter recognised by the Field Dog Stud Book.
